      <preamble>
         <formula name="enactingText">
            <p>The Scottish Ministers make the following Order in exercise of the powers conferred by section 4(1) of the Sea Fish (Conservation) Act 1967<noteRef href="#f00001" class="footnote" marker="1"/> and all other powers enabling them to do so.</p>
         </formula>
      </preamble>
      <body>
         <article eId="article-1">
            <heading>Citation, commencement and extent</heading>
            <num>1.</num>
            <paragraph eId="article-1-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>This Order may be cited as the Sea Fish Licensing (Foreign Vessels) (EU Exit) (Scotland) Order 2019 and comes into force on exit day.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="article-1-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>In this article “exit day” has the meaning given in section 20(1) of the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018<noteRef href="#f00002" class="footnote" marker="2"/>.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="article-1-3">
               <num>(3)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>This Order extends to Scotland only.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
         </article>
         <article eId="article-2">
            <heading>Prohibition on foreign boats fishing in the Scottish zone without a licence</heading>
            <num>2.</num>
            <paragraph eId="article-2-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>Fishing by foreign fishing boats within the Scottish zone is prohibited unless authorised by a licence granted by the Scottish Ministers.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="article-2-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>In this article, “foreign fishing boat” has the meaning given in section 4(12) of the Sea Fish (Conservation) Act 1967<noteRef href="#f00003" class="footnote" marker="3"/>.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
         </article>
